author = "Jeanmarie Mayer and Nimalie D. Stone and Molly Leecaster and Nan Hu and Warren Pettey and Matthew Samore and Susan M. Pacheco and Susan Sambol and Curtis Donskey and Annette Jencson and Kalpana Gupta and Judith Strymish and David Johnson and Christopher Woods and Edward Young and L. Clifford McDonald and Dale Gerding",
